{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/my-first-article/redis/redis6/","result":{"pageContext":{"article":{"banner":{"alt":"Redis","caption":"Photo by <u><a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/Nc5Q_CEcY44\">Redis</a></u>","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/ca4aa/redis_img.png","srcSet":"/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/77001/redis_img.png 75w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/4ec1c/redis_img.png 150w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/ca4aa/redis_img.png 300w","sizes":"(min-width: 300px) 300px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/dd377/redis_img.webp 75w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/40ac4/redis_img.webp 150w,\n/static/062c55607957fedfbebd3eaaab55825c/9e761/redis_img.webp 300w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 300px) 300px, 100vw"}]},"width":660,"height":400.40000000000003}}}},"body":"<h2>리더보드 기능</h2>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.30303030303031%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/7ae3e98f0cd03f9f0e18c9e894c22d38/c9b55/leaderboard.webp 165w,\n/static/7ae3e98f0cd03f9f0e18c9e894c22d38/f2908/leaderboard.webp 330w,\n/static/7ae3e98f0cd03f9f0e18c9e894c22d38/cc661/leaderboard.webp 660w,\n/static/7ae3e98f0cd03f9f0e18c9e894c22d38/f686e/leaderboard.webp 692w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/7ae3e98f0cd03f9f0e18c9e894c22d38/04c57/leaderboard.png 165w,\n/static/7ae3e98f0cd03f9f0e18c9e894c22d38/d9ecf/leaderboard.png 330w,\n/static/7ae3e98f0cd03f9f0e18c9e894c22d38/1f083/leaderboard.png 660w,\n/static/7ae3e98f0cd03f9f0e18c9e894c22d38/91e7e/leaderboard.png 692w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/7ae3e98f0cd03f9f0e18c9e894c22d38/1f083/leaderboard.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"EPL 순위표\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>EPL 순위표</p></figcaption>\n  </figure>\n리더보드란 실시간 랭킹을 볼수있는 기능이다. 위에 사진은 축구순위표여서 다르긴하지만 순위표라는 점에서 사진을 가져왔다. 게임분야에서는 점수순위, 랭크순위 검색엔진이라면 실시간검색순위 이커머스 분야라면 실시간 인기상품과 같은 기능들을 보여주기 위해 사용할 수 있다.</p>\n<h2>인기상품 리더보드 만들기</h2>\n<p>우리는 전에 redis에서 배웠던 SortedSet를 이용하여 리더보드를 만들어 볼까 한다.</p>\n<p>코드는 <a href=\"https://github.com/jiminchur/Study_Redis/tree/2-2\">👉🏻 GitHub 링크</a>에 들어가면 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>우리는 기능구현을 위한 부분만 보도록 하자.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>RedisConfig.java 파일 생성</li>\n<li>@Bean itemRedisTemplate() 작성</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">@Bean\npublic RedisTemplate&lt;String, ItemDto> rankTemplate (\n        RedisConnectionFactory redisConnectionFactory\n) {\n    RedisTemplate&lt;String, ItemDto> template = new RedisTemplate&lt;>();\n    template.setConnectionFactory(redisConnectionFactory);\n    // 주어진 데이터를 어떻게 직렬화 할것인지\n    template.setKeySerializer(RedisSerializer.string());\n    template.setValueSerializer(RedisSerializer.json());\n    return template;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>RedisTemplate으로 SortedSet을 사용한다면, ZSetOperations가 필요하다.</li>\n<li>ItemService.java 파일에 ZSetOperations 추가</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">@Slf4j\n@Service\n@RequiredArgsConstructor\npublic class ItemService {\n    private final ItemRepository itemRepository;\n    private final OrderRepository orderRepository;\n    private final ZSetOperations&lt;String, ItemDto> rankOps; // 추가\n    \n    public ItemService(\n            ItemRepository itemRepository,\n            OrderRepository orderRepository,\n            RedisTemplate&lt;String, ItemDto> rankTemplate // 추가\n    ) {\n        this.itemRepository = itemRepository;\n        this.orderRepository = orderRepository;\n        this.rankOps = rankTemplate.opsForZSet() // 추가\n    }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>기존 purchase 매서드에서 incrementScore 호출</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">public void purchase(Long id) {\n    Item item = itemRepository.findById(id)\n            .orElseThrow(() -> new ResponseStatusException(HttpStatus.NOT_FOUND));\n    orderRepository.save(ItemOrder.builder()\n            .item(item)\n            .count(1)\n            .build());\n    rankOps.incrementScore( // 추가\n            \"soldRanks\", \n            ItemDto.fromEntity(item), \n            1\n    );\n}</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>incrementScore 메서드는 SortedSet의 ZINCRBY 명령과 동일한 역할을 한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>만약 전달되는 데이터가 없더라도 추가하고 점수를 더해준다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>물품 반환하는 getMostSold 생성하기</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">public List&lt;ItemDto> getMostSold() {\n    Set&lt;ItemDto> ranks = rankOps.reverseRange(\"soldRanks\", 0, 9);\n    if (ranks == null) return Collections.emptyList();\n    return ranks.stream().toList();\n}</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>마지막으로 ItemController.java에 전체 순위표 출력하는 /ranks 생성하기</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">@GetMapping(\"/ranks\")\n    public List&lt;ItemDto> getRanks(){\n        return itemService.getMostSold();\n    }</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>테스트를 위해서 sql 쿼리문으로 데이터를 삽입해 놓았다. <a href=\"https://github.com/jiminchur/Study_Redis/blob/2-2/com.sparta.redis.rank/src/main/resources/data.sql\">👉🏻 해당 링크</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>POST요청으로 데이터 여러번 요청 후 Redis의 데이터 확인하기</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.84848484848484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/89efc6c217d1145178ce95a4e141a5f8/c9b55/ranks-redis.webp 165w,\n/static/89efc6c217d1145178ce95a4e141a5f8/f2908/ranks-redis.webp 330w,\n/static/89efc6c217d1145178ce95a4e141a5f8/cc661/ranks-redis.webp 660w,\n/static/89efc6c217d1145178ce95a4e141a5f8/6eb96/ranks-redis.webp 930w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/89efc6c217d1145178ce95a4e141a5f8/04c57/ranks-redis.png 165w,\n/static/89efc6c217d1145178ce95a4e141a5f8/d9ecf/ranks-redis.png 330w,\n/static/89efc6c217d1145178ce95a4e141a5f8/1f083/ranks-redis.png 660w,\n/static/89efc6c217d1145178ce95a4e141a5f8/416ee/ranks-redis.png 930w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/89efc6c217d1145178ce95a4e141a5f8/1f083/ranks-redis.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"Redis\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>Redis</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>순위표 출력하기</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 660px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 85.45454545454545%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/9df66714793dbe17b2d17950e436041d/c9b55/ranks.webp 165w,\n/static/9df66714793dbe17b2d17950e436041d/f2908/ranks.webp 330w,\n/static/9df66714793dbe17b2d17950e436041d/cc661/ranks.webp 660w,\n/static/9df66714793dbe17b2d17950e436041d/a66df/ranks.webp 990w,\n/static/9df66714793dbe17b2d17950e436041d/bf23a/ranks.webp 1314w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/9df66714793dbe17b2d17950e436041d/04c57/ranks.png 165w,\n/static/9df66714793dbe17b2d17950e436041d/d9ecf/ranks.png 330w,\n/static/9df66714793dbe17b2d17950e436041d/1f083/ranks.png 660w,\n/static/9df66714793dbe17b2d17950e436041d/7a3d6/ranks.png 990w,\n/static/9df66714793dbe17b2d17950e436041d/252a4/ranks.png 1314w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/9df66714793dbe17b2d17950e436041d/1f083/ranks.png\"\n            alt=\"스크린샷\"\n            title=\"GET - http://localhost:8080/items/ranks\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>GET - <a href=\"http://localhost:8080/items/ranks\">http://localhost:8080/items/ranks</a></p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>","categories":["ALL","Redis"],"date":"August 06, 2024","description":"Redis","id":"efb4e3a6-57ab-5975-ab70-af81f57c2350","keywords":["Redis","단기 심화 부트캠프","Sparta"],"slug":"/my-first-article/redis/redis6/","title":"[Redis] 리더보드와 Sorted Set","readingTime":{"text":"3 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3262260831","948380417"],"slicesMap":{}}